{"tid":1457580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極度懷疑標籤「散水撚」係分化計","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:51:52.000Z","uid":154245,"like":124,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"95dc800346975950ae12c52fac75e4b2212b5613","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"612到依家就經常係咁<br />\n前一秒開散水po<br />\n下一秒就開po屌散水<br />\n想點？<br />\n咁樣落去唔洗政府落手分化我地自己都會不和先<br />\n冇大台都可以搞lum你<br />\n成件事好鬼<br />\n認真呢d時候邊個唔會驚，特別經過琴日我地都知狗係冇底線，真心邊個都會驚<br />\n好多人願意企出黎已經好大勇氣<br />\n特別係呢d時候仲「自己人」鬧自己人真係好不智<br />\n成日話不被捕，be water<br />\n好啦依家做又有「人」開po屌<br />\n認真我地依家真係要團結，唔係互屌<br />\n散左水，咪吹雞再黎過<br />\n唔夠人，咪第二日再黎過<br />\n有咩所謂？<br />\n到依家運動持續左2個月<br />\n真係唔需要次次都去到盡<br />\n<br />\n我明大家壓力好大條氣好唔順<br />\n但係唔好發洩係自己手足身上啊<br />\n對自己人真係要多一分包容同埋理解<br />\n如果唔係你地同政府有咩分別啊？<br />\n如果唔係你地同中共有咩分別啊？<br />\n分分鐘仲差過佢哋啊<br />\n求下各位冷氣軍師手下留情<br />\n每日睇到蓮登咁真係好絕望<br />\n唔好搞到自己人唔開心先得㗎<br />\n槍口對外啊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f6d9db329d042db9399f124b5eea26631be9a2bb","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"b768c1aaf710ddc84567bd6d32c3276a9db2edc6","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d9db329d042db9399f124b5eea26631be9a2bb","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"e8a91667881b75239ef98d699985b96fe4f88c59","tid":1457580,"uid":254361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用個下腦諗嘢<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里而的大反派說了這麼幾句 <br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後這再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"e7eff2ad9103cfb8c09c241eaae0aafd4c8d3a42","tid":1457580,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"08f745edaec9a636a36b14631e6369b88b5f963f","tid":1457580,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"鬧完今晚就收聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化</span>"},{"pid":"12de45d0d7be02c0e23bc2ce003684bc5f1e087e","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b768c1aaf710ddc84567bd6d32c3276a9db2edc6","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d9db329d042db9399f124b5eea26631be9a2bb","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"f02b8080480e1d59d03aca16c8c4c7c15c0b9db6","tid":1457580,"uid":293698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4500f3b27eb06a0b7b900f0dff3e47e05ddab338","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12de45d0d7be02c0e23bc2ce003684bc5f1e087e","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b768c1aaf710ddc84567bd6d32c3276a9db2edc6","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d9db329d042db9399f124b5eea26631be9a2bb","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"香"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"0c82d3a26bb72743f2160507d842a54886f868bb","tid":1457580,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c93755aea73dfc42b10f939732656159d1efe6d","tid":1457580,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:31.000Z","msg":"有手足指出<br />\n<br />\n各位，先唔好理今日散定唔散，鬼定唔鬼<br />\n可唔可以將警方/政府刻意製作恐慌作為文宣？<br />\n無故取消航班，各種傳言，執法人員駐守，全部指向政府/警方<br />\n<br />\n例如，警方旗手入機場<br />\n唔理佢有冇做到，都要話咁樣係意味住佢哋的確有打算喺機場舉旗！<br />\n如果最後冇用到，係因為現場和平唔需要用。<br />\n如果有用到....<br />\n<br />\n大家可以諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8046df784054f876f7f881db6859574f236b2125","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02b8080480e1d59d03aca16c8c4c7c15c0b9db6","tid":1457580,"uid":293698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"依家佢哋屌緊散水啊<br />\n你真係覺得手足們唔會日日去？"},{"pid":"d00ebf82db8d70e5a3e785662df95457dad24975","tid":1457580,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b01bbc01babf13cc9a4e14b79dd7d2730a6a0900","tid":1457580,"uid":212182,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFpBSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFpBSm.jpg&h=c63b644e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好再鬧人散，唔好散播失敗，做得唔好反省下次做更好，內訌係無意思！！"},{"pid":"6ff1d1dab27b92afd4a666723600a6ba368ec6c2","tid":1457580,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"聽日再去"},{"pid":"44a1bc9d08ecb0856d49c98c3338220364df070f","tid":1457580,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"341a5e8bd2d49fb81762748e3365c13356b53d09","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4500f3b27eb06a0b7b900f0dff3e47e05ddab338","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12de45d0d7be02c0e23bc2ce003684bc5f1e087e","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b768c1aaf710ddc84567bd6d32c3276a9db2edc6","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"香"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"7c436c113dcff1d198e95a1417ca9bd05ec195e0","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"341a5e8bd2d49fb81762748e3365c13356b53d09","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4500f3b27eb06a0b7b900f0dff3e47e05ddab338","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12de45d0d7be02c0e23bc2ce003684bc5f1e087e","tid":1457580,"uid":154245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"香"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"港